Arab agreement on combating terrorism in the Egyptian capital on
April 22, Egypt's Middle East News Agency reported Friday.
</P>
<P>
The agreement is considered a basic and prominent step taken by
the Arab countries to face up to the challenge of terrorist
crimes. (Egypt-Terrorism-Arab Agreement) 
