crushed out in the doubles, and was substituted by Jiri Novak in
the reverse singles.
</P>
<P>
Czech Tennis Association (CTA) president and former Wimbledon
champion Jan Kodes severely criticized Savrda's use of Vacek.
</P>
<P>
The CTA is expected to find a new captain after a new executive
committee is elected on April 29.
</P>
<P>
Savrda led the Czechs to the 1996 semifinals of the Davis Cup,
and the quarterfinals last year. 
