<HEADLINE> Philippines to Speed Up Food Assistance Operations </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, April 17 (Xinhua) -- Local officials and the Philippine
national police in southern Mindanao were ordered Friday to speed
up the food assistance operations in areas hit by food crisis.
</P>
<P>
