The Portuguese PM was quoted by the Portuguese News Agency Lusa
as saying earlier this week that he had full confidence in Macao's
post-1999 future as a special administrative region of China.
</P>
<P>
Guterres said that his visit to Macao and China's inland areas
was meant to "create an atmosphere of confidence and
understanding." apart from "stimulating the presence of Portuguese
investment in China." 
