country because he felt disappointed of the future of Romanian
gymnastics.
</P>
<P>
Belu, who would extend his national coaching to the European
championships in St. Petersburg next month and the Goodwill Games
in New York in July, said that Romanian gymnastics no longer has a
future.
</P>
