States, where he runs a specialised school now after he coached
the U.S. Olympic team.
</P>
<P>
The 47-year-old Belu, who began coaching in Deva in 1981 and
was appointed national women's coach in 1990, has brought back
three world team titles with his gymnasts for Romania. 
